com.cognifide.qa.bb.mapper.field

Interface FieldProvider

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CurrentFrameProvider, DialogFieldProvider, PageObjectListProxyProvider, PageObjectSelectorListProxyProvider, ScopedPageObjectProvider, SelectorPageObjectProvider

    public interface FieldProvider
    Bobcat uses classes implementing FieldProvider interface as a source of values for the injected fields of classes (usually PageObjects).

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      boolean accepts(Field field)
      PageObjectInjectorListener calls this method to check if the provider is able to handle currently injected field, before it calls provideValue.
      Optional<Object> provideValue(Object pageObject, Field field, PageObjectContext context)
      PageObjectInjectorListener calls this method to get the value for the injected class field.

    • Method Detail

      • accepts

        boolean accepts(Field field)
        PageObjectInjectorListener calls this method to check if the provider is able to handle currently injected field, before it calls provideValue.
        Parameters:
        field - represents field in page object.
        Returns:
        true if provider is able to handle currently injected field.

      • provideValue

        Optional<Object> provideValue(Object pageObject,
                              Field field,
                              PageObjectContext context)
        PageObjectInjectorListener calls this method to get the value for the injected class field.
        Parameters:
        pageObject - This is the parent object of the injected field.
        field - Provider will generate value for this field.
        context - Provider might refer to frame path and locator factory while generating value for the field.
        Returns:
        Value for the injected field, as calculated by the provider.
